{"tid":1788692,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"200 萬名網友盲測手機相機 三星 Note10+ 奪冠 iPhone 11 Pro 首輪就被淘汰？","createTime":"2019-12-19T01:20:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T10:26:12.000Z","uid":141060,"like":6,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"4b0c05a16dd341f2c048db76b136eb8cd5a2f560","tid":1788692,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T01:20:06.000Z","msg":"看來 iPhone 11 Pro 的照片拍起來不夠討喜？<br />\n<br />\n知名科技 YouTuber Marques Brownlee（MKBHD）在 YouTube 上發布了一支手機相機的盲測影片，請網友評選自己比較喜歡哪張照片；只能說不愧是 MKBHD，參與者超過了 200 萬人！雖然照片都只有拍攝一張，但是參考價值應該還是滿高的～而這次參戰的共有 16 支手機，分別是 Google Pixel 4、Apple iPhone 11 Pro、Samsung Galaxy Note10+、Google Pixel 3a、Samsung Galaxy S10e、One Plus 7T Pro、One Plus 7T、華為 Mate 30 Pro、華為 P30 Pro、小米 Note10、Sony Xperia 1、Redmi K20 Pro（台灣名為小米 9T Pro）、LG G8X ThinQ、華碩 ROG Phone II、華碩 ZenFone 6 和 Royale Flexpai（柔派摺疊手機）。連柔派都出現了，應該沒什麼手機遺漏了吧？第一輪比的是人像的拍攝，同時要顧及後方背景的成像表現<br />\n<img src=\"https://agirls.aottercdn.com/media/4f91fb01-83e0-48d7-a7cb-db5520758e78.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fagirls.aottercdn.com%2Fmedia%2F4f91fb01-83e0-48d7-a7cb-db5520758e78.jpg&h=81006f74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼藍字表示勝出<br />\n<img src=\"https://agirls.aottercdn.com/media/b92bfede-bc2d-43b4-99ff-e43b07cf01ac.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fagirls.aottercdn.com%2Fmedia%2Fb92bfede-bc2d-43b4-99ff-e43b07cf01ac.PNG&h=07406871&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://agirls.aottercdn.com/media/c0fd6a76-a5ce-411e-85e8-e38db5df5f9b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fagirls.aottercdn.com%2Fmedia%2Fc0fd6a76-a5ce-411e-85e8-e38db5df5f9b.png&h=9b829136&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://agirls.aottercdn.com/media/aec34e7d-7686-4c00-8fc5-4d4a63556344.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fagirls.aottercdn.com%2Fmedia%2Faec34e7d-7686-4c00-8fc5-4d4a63556344.png&h=35c5b81c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://agirls.aottercdn.com/media/ec0642dc-e884-40d0-a746-dbf32849b16e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fagirls.aottercdn.com%2Fmedia%2Fec0642dc-e884-40d0-a746-dbf32849b16e.png&h=0062da7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沒想到第一輪就大爆冷門？可能比較有爭議的就是 iPhone 11 Pro 輸給了 One Plus 7T Pro（iPhone 的成色過於寫實？），還有 Sony Xperia 1 不知為何照片對比度偏低，敗給了 Google Pixel 4，還有儘管華為 Mate 30 Pro 贏過了 ROG Phone II，P30 Pro 卻輸給了 Redmi K20 Pro<br />\n<img src=\"https://agirls.aottercdn.com/media/52cdb32b-2c53-4848-8d7b-c8a73d9883d8.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fagirls.aottercdn.com%2Fmedia%2F52cdb32b-2c53-4848-8d7b-c8a73d9883d8.PNG&h=daeeb36a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://agirls.aottercdn.com/media/cdcfba56-68d5-4adc-8944-168437ddf3a7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fagirls.aottercdn.com%2Fmedia%2Fcdcfba56-68d5-4adc-8944-168437ddf3a7.png&h=362cb13e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://agirls.aottercdn.com/media/21ab0f81-8786-42f5-b7f9-67f91e6edf09.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fagirls.aottercdn.com%2Fmedia%2F21ab0f81-8786-42f5-b7f9-67f91e6edf09.png&h=05ee90c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://agirls.aottercdn.com/media/5b719a8b-a44a-46a9-8748-78a84d5bfcad.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fagirls.aottercdn.com%2Fmedia%2F5b719a8b-a44a-46a9-8748-78a84d5bfcad.png&h=49d7b705&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第二輪表現應該就比較正常了&hellip;吧&hellip;？第二輪是手拿物品的照片，要同時檢視物品跟人的手、以及背景的色澤。勝出的分別是 Mate30 Pro、Note10+、S10e、Pixel 4。最後兩輪的結果，Note10+ 打敗了 Mate 30 Pro、S10e 打敗了 Pixel 4，變成三星打三星的局面；最後的一張風景照決勝負，Note10+ 擊敗 S10e 奪得了冠軍<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/KxsFat1ImiY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKxsFat1ImiY&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6udFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=2a2ebd97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/KxsFat1ImiY</a><br />\nMKBHD 統整後表示，用戶多半偏好明亮的照片，另外景深效果並不一定討人喜歡，用戶反而更偏好主體、背景都很清晰的照片，他推判這是華為手機、Pixel 4 敗下陣的主因。另外，這四輪比賽的照片都在白天拍攝，關於夜拍、多鏡頭運用等其實並沒有著墨太多；還有可能都是在手機上看照片，其實不會看到太多的細節表現，所以要是自己的手機輸了也不用太難過 XD 但你如果常發 IG，大概就知道買哪幾款手機，獲得的讚數會比較高了！"},{"pid":"956c92c011a692e575957874bb5fc3e9ebce4376","tid":1788692,"uid":311583,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T01:23:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6udFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=04d00b78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tax87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftax87&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6udFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=316f23b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tax87</a><br />\n<br />\n請推po<br />\n<br />\n【核彈】呢個方法可以防水炮車【行動po求推】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1778898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1778898</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"953164f279429e3d19fa3271fbe41cd32382c7d1","tid":1788692,"uid":105678,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T01:28:05.000Z","msg":"MKBHD都幾出名，上次先同Elon musk合作完<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e06f1de03cf94230f623da6bfc3bc81c1d54384","tid":1788692,"uid":11593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"953164f279429e3d19fa3271fbe41cd32382c7d1","tid":1788692,"uid":105678,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T01:28:05.000Z","msg":"MKBHD都幾出名，上次先同Elon musk合作完<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T01:57:35.000Z","msg":"佢岩岩過左1千萬個youtube subscriber 好撚癲<img src=\"/asse